    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:tracking-tight lg:text-6xl">
            About <span class="text-blue-600">Peopertease</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
            Connecting dreams to addresses since @DateTime.Now.Year
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-24">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                <div class="p-3 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Founded by Subarna Guragai, Peopertease began as a vision to revolutionize the real estate industry through technology. What started as a simple idea has grown into a comprehensive platform that serves thousands of clients looking to buy, sell, or rent properties.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
                Our journey has been marked by innovation, customer satisfaction, and a relentless pursuit of excellence in the real estate sector.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/about-office.jpg")" alt="Peopertease office" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
        </div>
    </div>

