            <div class="md:w-3/4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Subarna Guragai</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium mb-4">Software Developer & Real Estate Enthusiast</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    With a strong background in software development and a passion for real estate, Subarna Guragai founded Peopertease to bridge the gap between technology and property transactions. Her expertise in building scalable web applications combined with her understanding of the real estate market has been instrumental in creating this innovative platform.
